        "message": "LU-5420 mgc: MGC should retry for invalid import\n\nSince mgc import is not fully replayable, i.e. the import might\nbe evicted during recovery, so mgc_enqueue (for retrieving config\nlog) should retry until the import is fully recovered or closed.\n\nSigned-off-by: Wang Di <di.wang@intel.com>\nChange-Id: I8dbcafbda362ebbd3370e7527a3c14c5942fde96\n"
